metadata.name: MOON
metadata.description:
"It takes two to tango", they say.  
The pieces in this brand new collection dance better together, in pairs, but they are also ready to dance solo.

Professionally a designer, photography is a very organic extension of my work, for 20 years. I believe I have a specific style and point of view, coming from design, translated into my pieces. I wanted to melt my 2 passions into one ongoing collection, to push my limits, and get out of my comfort zone, while delivering something fresh and different, as I refuse to put myself in a box.
